# Testing Strategy

The project uses the official JSON Calendar test cases for validation and compliance:

## Test Specifications
- [spec/1.0.json](mdc:spec/1.0.json) contains the comprehensive test suite for JSON Calendar 1.0 specification
- Each test case validates different aspects of the JSON Calendar format including:
  - Event creation and modification
  - Date and time handling
  - Calendar properties
  - Timezone support

## Running Tests
Tests can be executed using the npm scripts defined in [package.json](mdc:package.json). The test suite ensures that the TypeScript implementation correctly handles all specification cases.
